</p><p>The findings of the present study are for psychologists and group therapists for a permanent psychological treatment after detoxification and provide effective interventions for relapse prevention and main difficulties before and after detoxification stage in MMT.</p></fn><fn id="afn4169" fn-type="other"><p>
